name: Youmna
greetingText: I really like your sense of humor, your eyes, your laugh, and everything about you
wishText: I truly hope you achieve all your dreams and everything your heart is working toward. Even if we’re not together, I want you to know that I’m still wishing you happiness and peace in your life. I’m really proud of you of who you are and how far you’ve come and I always will be, Stay kind.
